[texton w=1]
We dwarves have strict restrictions on marrying other races, in order to keep our bloodlines alive.[k]
It is especially strict for girls, who must obtain special permission from the chief to marry a man from the outside world.[k]
It also isn't allowed to remain single forever. At a certain age, we must return and marry a man from our village.[k]
To live in a village and bear children... That is the role of us dwarf women...[k]
[textoff]
@w05
