;◇主人公イベント・結婚イベント（指輪が２つそろうと発生）
*theo_wedding

; ドワーフ村
@out
@w05
@bg f=0028
@mu f=highland
@saveon
[texton w=1]
A few days later.[k]
I visited a dwarf village with [フレデリカ].[k]
In order to stay with [フレデリカ] as long as possible, I accompanied her on her trip back home.[k]
The village of the dwarves was located deep in inhospitable remote mountains, and it took many days to reach it.[k]
In the village, I also greeted the chief as [フレデリカ]'s fiancé. The chief agreed to our future marriage on the condition that [フレデリカ] first give birth to a dwarf child.[k]
Surprisingly, I was welcomed by the dwarven villagers and allowed to stay in the village for one night.[k]
And on the same day, [フレデリカ] was to marry a dwarf man.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

@fg c=フレデリカ e=通常 f=29 b
@bgf f=0010
[texton w=1]
[テオ e=通常 f=12]「Not one, but six?!」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd253 f=29]「Yes, in order to have children quickly and reliably, temporary brides marry six men at once...」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
To my surprise, [フレデリカ] suddenly married several men.[k]
With certain partners, it may be difficult to conceive. Therefore, it is the practice in this village to have them marry more than one man.[k]
The marriage period is until a child is conceived and delivered. In the event that a woman fails to conceive a child after six months of procreation here, she is to be released from her obligation at that time.[k]
[テオ f=10]「Well... are you okay with suddenly marrying several men?」[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=34
[フレデリカ v=vd254 f=34]「It's okay. All the girls in this village do it. Besides, all the husbands are very kind people.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
From now on, [フレデリカ] will live with her six husbands in a large common house in the village.[k]
There are other girls here in similar circumstances, so multiple men and women will be trying to procreate on a daily basis.[k]
The six husbands who married [フレデリカ] are all grown men with a track record of impregnating a number of women already.[k]
They are very practiced with women. So they'll surely safely make a baby with her. But...[k]
[テオ f=09]「Damn...!」[k]
My chest is pounding. My heart is stirred with anxiety.[k]
From now on, [フレデリカ] will have to take turns with her dwarven husbands on a daily basis in order to procreate.[k]
But that's the role she has to play, for the survival of her people.[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
It is very painful, but I have to endure it. I have to wait until the day she comes back to me.[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=01
[フレデリカ v=vd255 f=01]「It's okay. Captain!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?」[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=02
[フレデリカ v=vd256 f=02]「I will never forget you. So, please believe in me and wait for me.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「[フレデリカ]...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Okay. I'll be waiting for you.」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd257 f=02]「Okay, I'm off...」[k]
[textoff]
@cl
@w05
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=05]「[フレデリカ]...」[k]
[フレデリカ] entered her new home. The residence where her six husbands were waiting for her.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I silently watched her back as she left, then departed from the dwarf village...[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w1

; １週間後・サファイアシティの宿屋
@bg f=0001
@mu f=calm
[texton w=0]
It's been a week since I returned from the dwarf village.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
I want to see [フレデリカ]. I couldn't hold back that feeling anymore.[k]
No man of another race is allowed to meet a dwarf girl who is aiming for a baby. If they had sex, a pure blooded dwarf may not be born.[k]
But my feelings for her drove me to her dwarf village.[k]
I don't care if I can't talk to her. I want to see [フレデリカ], at least for a moment. I want to burn her image into my eyes.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1

; ドワーフ村
@bg f=0010
[texton w=0]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
When I arrived at the dwarf village, I approached the residence where [フレデリカ] and her six husbands lived.[k]
Then, avoiding the eyes of dwarves, I went around to the back of the house.[k]
Is there anywhere I can get a glimpse of what's going on inside...?[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
